Interface DeployedDevice

All Superinterfaces:
org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier

DeployedDeviceImpl
public interface DeployedDevice extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
A representation of the model object 'Deployed Device'.

The following features are supported:

  • Metadata
  • Mac Address
  • Network Interface
  • Mac Protocol
  • Base Property
